    <text type="letter" xml:lang="ru" xml:id="letter-01112">
        <body>
            <opener>
            <salute rend="inline">
               <persName ref="people.xml#pan01">Никита
                        Иванович!</persName>
            </salute>
         </opener>
            <p>Письмо Ваше получила, и что любезнейший <persName ref="people.xml#pau01">сын</persName> мой в вожделенном здравии находится, сердечно радуюсь, желая
                продолжения его здравия; впрочем, пребываю Вам Нашею Императорскою милостию
                благосклонна.</p>
            <closer>
            <signed>
               <persName ref="people.xml#cat01">Екатерина.</persName>
            </signed>
         </closer>
            <postscript>
                <p>
               <persName ref="people.xml#ela01">Елагин</persName> поехал в город; я сама
                    распечатала Ваш пакет.</p>
            </postscript>
           <closer> 
            <dateline>
               <date when-custom="1763-11-23">23 Ноября, 1763 г.</date>
                <placeName ref="places.xml#tsa01">Царское Село.</placeName>
            </dateline>
         </closer>
        </body>
    </text>

            <text type="translation" xml:lang="en">
                <body>
                    <opener>
                        <salute rend="inline">
                            <persName ref="people.xml#pan01">Nikita Ivanovich!</persName>
                        </salute>
                    </opener>
                    <p>I have received your letter, and I am sincerely glad that my dearest <persName ref="people.xml#pau01">son</persName> is in desired good health, and I wish for the continuation of his well-being; in any case, I remain gracious to you with Our Imperial favor.</p>
                    <closer>
                        <signed>
                            <persName ref="people.xml#cat01">Catherine.</persName>
                        </signed>
                    </closer>
                    <postscript>
                        <p>
                            <persName ref="people.xml#ela01">Elagin</persName> went to the city; I opened your packet myself.
                        </p>
                    </postscript>
                    <closer>
                        <dateline>
                            <date when-custom="1763-11-23">23 November, 1763</date>
                            <placeName ref="places.xml#tsa01">Tsarskoe Selo.</placeName>
                        </dateline>
                    </closer>
                </body>
            </text>

        </group>
